htsjdk.variant.variantcontext.filter

Class FilteringIterator

  • java.lang.Object
    • htsjdk.variant.variantcontext.filter.FilteringIterator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CloseableIterator<VariantContext>, java.io.Closeable, java.lang.AutoCloseable, java.lang.Iterable<VariantContext>, java.util.Iterator<VariantContext>

    public class FilteringIterator
extends java.lang.Object
implements CloseableIterator<VariantContext>, java.lang.Iterable<VariantContext>
    A filtering iterator for VariantContexts that takes a base iterator and a VariantContextFilter. The iterator returns all the variantcontexts for which the filter's function "test" returns true (and only those)
    Author:
    Yossi Farjoun
